   364	
   365	    DEC-V61-052 Batch D: mirrors _load_ldc_vortex_gold's shape.
   366	    Returns {value, tolerance, source, literature_doi} or None.
   367	    """
   368	    gold_path = _GOLD_ROOT / "backward_facing_step.yaml"
